FLKS you had to own this stock on 41719 to vote record date Anybody who exited after will not be voting yes or no They will be submitting a broker nonvote That does not go toward the 50 Thats why theyre having trouble getting this approved despite the fact that everybody who currently owns wants it to go through They need 9mm yes votes to pass this 26mm shares changed hands since 41719 A large amount of those shares changed hands several times You have to hope that its well less than 9mm shares changing hands and everybody who held from April to now submits their vote
